CatDescriptText: image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1963, pg. 7 reads: "D.I. Hostesses - A bevy of charming young maids and matrons, added lustre to the formal dance at the Webster. Left to right; Olivia Maston, Alberta Thompson, Vera Thompson, Ella Baker, wife of the Pirate star; Marie Francis, Marlene Thomas and Yvonne Kemp. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: D. I. members, from left: Olivia Maston, Alberta Thompson, Vera Thompson (Matthews), Ella Baker, Marie Francis, Marlene Thomas wearing floral halter gown and light colored elbow length gloves, and Yvonne Jones Kemp, standing in row in Hotel Webster Hall for D. I. ball
